{{Weapon}}

== Overview ==
This tank-like weapon fires a large shard of depleted colonite, which does large amounts armor damage. The reloading process however takes some amount of time and energy.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Shard Cannon can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
